{"tid":146969,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺一個人生只要點爆運氣值就屈哂機？","createTime":"2017-03-07T13:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T17:07:52.000Z","uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0f9ab428f792d1be75469b64c2ed7c1610764e","tid":146969,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話努力、知識係可以改變命運<br />\n<br />\n根本實力、努力呢啲野都係睇天資同運氣<br />\n運氣唔係話買六合彩中唔中、估公定字咁簡單。由運氣提供既環境因素係最緊要。點解你會有努力呢個心？點解我個fd又沉迷打機，我又沉迷打機，佢會係考之前睇兩眼合格，我就要肥？<br />\n<br />\n例如一個家庭，個老豆死左，得返老母返工，你要努力既決心好大機會會比一個生於健全家庭既人大幾倍。配合埋冇fd、冇女呢啲因素、加埋有努力既天份，就會成為一個努力既天才。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n父幹、人際關係、際遇、個樣比人既感覺、老闆好唔好人、有冇得升職、面試果陣有冇人做你對手、係公廁柯屎有冇廁紙、條女有冇豬、個閪臭唔臭<br />\n<br />\n全部都係運氣<img src=\"http:// forum8.hkgolden .com/faces/lomore/@.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F%20forum8.hkgolden%20.com%2Ffaces%2Flomore%2F%40.gif%20&h=252315c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84318d68863365271d8eac6c07c489913c66b6f2","tid":146969,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d8e8ccd019101c6829ef906af85b2a731744877","tid":146969,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉你on9少陣啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5718ea8d901ebab548962616e5b93556e12da10","tid":146969,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"認真po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd22b287070b2f149f6746d3e7ea855ac208227","tid":146969,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知咩"},{"pid":"7afed9dffaf488f82b8457ed747843720acb5259","tid":146969,"uid":40409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:05:57.000Z","msg